title: Lead Destiny
description: A man with many names and no purpose meets a woman with an iron will and a singular goal. The two form an unlikely bond as they work together to fight the gang they have both been wronged by and their mysterious and powerful leader, a man with no eyes and psychic powers. Travel Wild West Wyoming with Cassidy and the Man of Many Names while taking a deep delve into the psyche of the narrator and the horrors of his own creation.
author: Sean  Morrison
